        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Help Hospitals Recover Act of 2005 - Directs the Director of the Federal Emeregency Management Agency to make a described payment to each private or public hospital that temporarily ceased to operate because of a mandatory evacuation order issued in anticipation of Hurricane Rita.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
